classes.name: SessionCommandMixin
classes.docstring: A class mixin for command classes needing _build_session().

classes.name: IndexGroupCommand
classes.docstring:
Abstract base class for commands with the index_group options.

This also corresponds to the commands that permit the pip version check.

methods.name: handle_pip_version_check
